alogService/ListProducts,72.89308422962807,104.31690251572327,出现次数:3\naiops-k8s-05,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-2,checkoutservice-2,hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote,9347.601322014976,49143.75,出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.CurrencyService/GetSupportedCurrencies,2962.6538829510814,4055.346153846154,出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-01,emailservice,checkoutservice-2,emailservice-1,/hipstershop.EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation,699.5782184205979,1862.5,出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-07,shippingservice,checkoutservice-2,shippingservice-1,hipstershop.ShippingService/ShipOrder,231.7208354822073,933.5,出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-06,productcatalogservice,checkoutservice-2,productcatalogservice-1,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,9648.811239171926,18906.5,出现次数:2\naiops-k8s-08,productcatalogservice,checkoutservice-2,productcatalogservice-0,hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct,10309.246181528531,20785.0,出现次数:2\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-1", "frontend-0", "frontend-1", "frontend-2", "productcatalogservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-0", "shippingservice-1"], "service_name": ["checkoutservice", "emailservice", "frontend", "productcatalogservice", "recommendationservice", "shippingservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-01", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-05", "aiops-k8s-06", "aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-08"]}, "status_combinations": "node_name,service_name,parent_pod,child_pod,operation_name,status_code,status_message,occurrence_count\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-0,frontend-0,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,14,\"connection error: desc = \"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.8.174:9555: connect: connection refused\"\"\",出现次数:489\naiops-k8s-01,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,14,\"connection error: desc = \"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.8.174:9555: connect: connection refused\"\"\",出现次数:380\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,14,\"connection error: desc = \"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.8.174:9555: connect: connection refused\"\"\",出现次数:357\naiops-k8s-01,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,14,transport is closing,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-0,frontend-0,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,14,transport is closing,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,14,transport is closing,出现次数:1\n", "matched_anomaly": "Please analyze the abnormal event between 2025-06-18T20:10:06Z and 2025-06-18T20:26:06Z and provide the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-18 20:10:06+00:00 to 2025-06-18 20:26:06+00:00"}, "trace_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "### 分析结果\n\n从日志数据中，我发现了以下关键异常模式：\n\n1. **连接拒绝错误**：多个 `frontend` 服务的实例（`frontend-0`, `frontend-1`, `frontend-2`）报告了相同的错误，即尝试连接到 `10.233.8.174:9555` 时被拒绝。\n2. **传输关闭错误**：部分日志显示 `transport is closing`，表明连接在尝试建立时被中断。\n\n### 关键发现\n- **被抱怨的服务**：日志中提到的目标地址是 `10.233.8.174:9555`，但未明确服务名称。这可能是一个内部服务（如 `adservice`）。\n- **错误类型**：`connection refused` 和 `transport is closing` 表明目标服务可能未运行或端口配置错误。\n\n### 输出 JSON\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"connection refused\", \"transport is closing\", \"transport: Error while dialing\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"目标服务（可能是 adservice）的端口 9555 配置错误或服务未运行，导致连接被拒绝。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.8.174:9555: connect: connection refused\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend 服务在尝试调用目标服务时遇到传输关闭错误，可能是目标服务突然终止。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = transport is closing\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 下一步建议\n1. **验证目标服务**：确认 `10.233.8.174:9555` 对应的服务名称及其健康状态。\n2. **检查端口配置**：确保目标服务的端口配置正确且服务正在运行。\n3. **排查网络问题**：检查网络连接是否稳定，避免因网络问题导致连接中断。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的调用链数据，我现在进行全面的异常扫描分析。让我仔细分析这些数据来识别显著的异常模式。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->adservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->recommendationservice\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"所有frontend实例对adservice的调用都出现connection refused错误，错误码14，连接被拒绝，表明adservice服务完全不可用\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice->shippingservice调用延迟从9347ms激增至49143ms，延迟倍数5.26倍，显著延迟\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice调用延迟从9648ms增至18906ms，延迟倍数1.96倍；从10309ms增至20785ms，延迟倍数2.02倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend->recommendationservice调用延迟从4106ms增至3628ms，虽然绝对延迟降低但异常频次高(19次)，且下游productcatalogservice也受影响\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n1. **最严重的异常**：adservice完全不可用，所有frontend实例都无法连接，这是明确的根因服务故障。\n\n2. **显著的延迟瓶颈**：\n   - shippingservice出现严重延迟（5.26倍增长）\n   - productcatalogservice出现中度延迟（2倍增长）\n   - recommendationservice及其下游productcatalogservice存在异常调用模式\n\n3. **错误传播路径**：adservice的故障直接影响所有frontend实例，而shippingservice和productcatalogservice的延迟问题主要影响checkout流程。\n\n这些异常模式表明系统存在多个服务层面的性能问题，需要进一步深入分析各服务间的依赖关系和影响范围。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于对异常事件时间窗口的指标数据分析，我发现了多个显著的异常模式。以下是详细的扫描结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\",\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"region_pending\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"request\",\n    \"response\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_usage_rate 显著异常，从41.5%上升到57.16%，变化率31.75%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"节点内存使用率异常升高，正常中位数41.5%，故障中位数57.16%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-07\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes 大幅下降，可用内存减少28.6%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"可用内存从10.4GB减少到7.54GB，变化率31.91%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"region_pending 队列积压异常，变化率33.55%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"region_pending 从13049减少到9299.5，但可能表明IO处理异常\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 响应时间显著恶化，p99变化率146.09%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"最大响应时间p99从12208ms飙升到78376ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"request 和 response 流量急剧下降，变化率超过144%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"请求量从298下降到48，响应量从300下降到48\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 响应时间异常，p99变化率129.61%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"最大响应时间p99从9664ms上升到45249ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 响应时间恶化，p99变化率131.17%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"最大响应时间p99从6881ms上升到33109ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage 出现异常变化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CPU使用率p99从0.09上升到0.13，变化率32.95%\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n1. **节点级资源问题**：aiops-k8s-04和aiops-k8s-07节点出现内存使用异常\n2. **数据库性能问题**：TiDB TikV组件的region_pending队列异常\n3. **服务级延迟问题**：多个微服务（currencyservice、emailservice、shippingservice）出现响应时间显著恶化\n4. **流量异常**：adservice-2实例的请求和响应流量急剧下降\n5. **容器资源使用**：redis-cart-0的CPU使用率出现异常变化\n\n这些异常模式表明系统在多个层面出现了性能问题，需要进一步深入分析确定根因。"}
